---
title: Japanese-Style Chicken Meatballs with Garlic Rice
description: Sweet and sticky, mirin and honey add kid-friendly flavour to savoury-glazed meatballs! Tsukene are traditionally skewered and grilled over charcoal, but our meatballs are broiled for similar results!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-poulet-a-la-japonaise-d758d929.jpg
